name: Supper Antibody
description: This game is a submission for the Stay Safe! jam, um i must say this game was a hella ride to make and i had to rush with this one since the jam started near midnight and i didn't have a lot of time to make it so treat these game as a early access prototype which needs more work the site says i had 1 more day to finish the game but truly i did not, also there well be a postmortem on my YouTube https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5X7ZlWAoFNej0j6PSGF0Zg
